      "audio_url": "https://thdlkizjbpwdndtggleb.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/game-assets/tts/1783007699708_SurvivorNPC_ThreatWarning.mp3",
      "text": "Stay still. Don't run. The Raptors track movement — fast movement triggers the chase reflex. Back away slowly, keep your eyes forward, and find cover before they close the distance. You have maybe thirty seconds.",
